我当了你多少年女友抚慰专员

312
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:57,470
February,2005.
2005年 2月

313
00:16:57,470 --> 00:17:01,090
I had just come back from a marathon study session at the law library.
我在法律图书馆漫长的课 刚结束回来

314
00:17:01,090 --> 00:17:03,860
Hey. Hey,Natalie,where's,uh,where's Ted?
嘿 Natalie Ted在哪儿?

315
00:17:03,860 --> 00:17:08,250
We broke up... again!
我们... 又分手了!

316
00:17:10,350 --> 00:17:14,680
Won't you sit with me for a little while? Just sit?
你能不能坐这儿陪我一会? 坐着就好?

317
00:17:14,680 --> 00:17:17,440
Man,you know what? I've been up for,like,36 hours.
大小姐 你要知道 我大概有 36个小时没睡过了

318
00:17:21,530 --> 00:17:23,300
Just for a few minutes.
就几分钟

319
00:17:28,980 --> 00:17:31,740
And at first,I was completely sympathetic.
一开始 我很有同情心

320
00:17:31,740 --> 00:17:35,270
But damn it,Ted,over the years,you made me cynical.
不过Ted 他妈的搞了这么多年 你把我逼得铁石心肠了

321
00:17:35,270 --> 00:17:37,420
You know what? I'm going to go get us some Rocky Road,
我去搞点石板街蛋糕过来

322
00:17:37,420 --> 00:17:41,120
and we're just going to sit here and talk it out until it makes sense.
我们就坐在这儿 陪聊到你想通为止

323
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:45,350
I just thought we had something so special,you know?
我以为我们有特别之处 你知道吗?

324
00:17:45,890 --> 00:17:47,840
Me,too. Yeah.
我理解 嗯

325
00:17:47,840 --> 00:17:51,320
But,you know,life goes on,sweetheart.
但是 你知道 生活还得继续  亲爱的

326
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:54,560
I don't know how I'm going to put my life back together after this.
我不知道分了手我要怎么过下去

327
00:17:54,560 --> 00:17:57,090
Oh,shut up.
哦 闭嘴

328
00:17:58,310 --> 00:17:59,870
Well,I'm sorry my search for true love
很抱歉因为我寻找真爱之旅

329
00:17:59,870 --> 00:18:02,260
has been such an inconvenience to you guys.
给你们添了这么多麻烦

330
00:18:02,260 --> 00:18:04,650
You know what? Maybe your precious pictures
要知道 说不定你那些珍贵的照片

331
00:18:04,650 --> 00:18:06,430
would look a lot better if I wasn't in them.
少了我会更好

332
00:18:06,430 --> 00:18:08,030
They'd look a lot better if Marshall weren't in them.
如果少了Marshall会更好

333
00:18:08,030 --> 00:18:10,530
Cheap shot,bro. Cheap shot.
贱招儿 贱招儿

334
00:18:10,530 --> 00:18:12,020
You know what these pictures are,Lily?
你知道这些照片是什么吗 Lily?

335
00:18:12,020 --> 00:18:15,390
They're a big,fat lie. They're posed. They're touched up.
是彻彻底底的谎言 都是做出来的 都做过手脚

336
00:18:15,390 --> 00:18:17,470
They're what you want our life to be,not what it is.
是你期望中的生活 而不是真实的情况

337
00:18:17,470 --> 00:18:19,360
- That's not true! - Oh,yeah?
- 乱讲! - 是吗?

338
00:18:19,360 --> 00:18:22,550
Okay. Look at this one. Halloween,two years ago.
看这张 两年前万圣节前夜

339
00:18:22,550 --> 00:18:24,080
You and Marshall got in a huge fight
你和Marshall大吵一架

340
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:25,640
because you didn't want to dress up as penguins.
因为你不想穿成企鹅

341
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:27,290
No,no-no,it's not just that she didn't want to.
不是 不是 不是她不想穿

342
00:18:27,290 --> 00:18:30,390
It's that she called penguins "lame. " Penguins.
是她觉得企鹅是很傻的 企鹅

343
00:18:30,390 --> 00:18:35,100
And yet,here you are,smiling like nothing's wrong - completely phony.
但是你还笑得像什么事都没有一样 太假了

344
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:38,230
Robin's birthday,three years ago.
三年前 Robin生日

345
00:18:38,230 --> 00:18:40,240
Robin had a cold and you made her change
Robin感冒了 你逼她把睡衣换了

346
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:41,840
out of her pajama's for the picture.
拍照片

347
00:18:41,840 --> 00:18:44,690
And then you pinched my cheeks really hard to get some color in them.
你还使劲捏我的脸 搞点血色出来

348
00:18:44,690 --> 00:18:46,650
Yeah,but you look pretty.
是的 但是看上去美美的

349
00:18:47,550 --> 00:18:50,120
And then,we all ate chocolate cake in my bed.
后来大家在我的床上吃巧克力蛋糕

350
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:53,400
- Actually,that was a really nice night. - Yeah,it was.
- 其实那天晚上很开心 - 嗯 确实

351
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:55,690
Yeah,I guess it was.
是啊 是的 (友谊万岁)

352
00:18:55,690 --> 00:18:58,050
Hey,look at this one.
看这张

353
00:18:58,470 --> 00:19:01,480
This is the first picture the three of us ever took together.
这是我们三个一起拍的第一张照片

354
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:03,280
That's right. It was.
对哦 是的耶

355
00:19:03,280 --> 00:19:05,540
Yeah,you remember how it happened?
嗯 你记得当时什么情况吗?

356
00:19:05,540 --> 00:19:07,310
Okay,ready?
好 准备好了吗?

357
00:19:07,310 --> 00:19:10,930
Wait,wait,wait. What pose should we do? Buddy cop picture?
等等 等等 我们拗什么造型? 警探拍档剧照?

358
00:19:11,980 --> 00:19:15,930
Oh,no,no-no! What about,um,'80s sitcom about two roommates who never agree on anything?
不 不要 不要! 80年代拍那个两个 总是对着干的室友的肥皂剧呢?

359
00:19:17,760 --> 00:19:20,950
Nice. Okay,one,two...
不错 好 一 二... 

360
00:19:22,490 --> 00:19:24,810
Hi,Marshall. Ready for the movie?
嗨 Marshall 准备好去看电影了吗?

361
00:19:24,810 --> 00:19:27,840
Um,yeah. Just a second though,okay? We're about to make history.
去啊 就等一会儿 好吗? 我们要记录历史性的一刻

362
00:19:27,840 --> 00:19:30,310
We're about to take our first ever roommate picture.
我们要拍第一张室友合照

363
00:19:30,310 --> 00:19:32,910
Yeah. Hey,why don't you get in the picture,too?
对 要不你也一起来拍吧?

364
00:19:32,910 --> 00:19:34,740
- Really? - Yeah.
- 真的? - 真的

365
00:19:34,740 --> 00:19:37,340
What are you doing,Ted? What if we break up?
你干什么 Ted? 要是我们分手了怎么办?

366
00:19:37,340 --> 00:19:39,370
What if you don't?
要是不分手呢?

367
00:19:40,180 --> 00:19:42,460
Come on. Come on.
来吧 来吧

368
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:47,560
I forgot all about that.
我都快忘了

369
00:19:47,560 --> 00:19:50,380
Marshall and I had just been dating a few weeks
Marshall和我刚交往几个星期

370
00:19:51,070 --> 00:19:53,870
and you invited me into the picture.
你请我一起拍照片

371
00:19:54,550 --> 00:19:56,060
I liked you.
我喜欢你嘛

372
00:19:56,060 --> 00:19:58,040
- We have to get Amanda back. - Really?
- 我们得叫Amanda回来 - 真的?

373
00:19:58,040 --> 00:20:01,580
Ted,you believed in me. It's my turn to believe in you.
Ted 你相信我 这次轮到我相信你了

374
00:20:01,580 --> 00:20:04,360
For all I know,she's the one.
我知道她一定能成

375
00:20:04,360 --> 00:20:05,770
Thanks,Lil.
谢谢 Lily 

376
00:20:05,770 --> 00:20:09,270
I think Lori's age has made her very wise.
我觉得Lori的年纪让她长不少脑子

377
00:20:09,270 --> 00:20:12,040
They say your forties are when you really get to know yourself.
他们说40岁的时候 你才能真正了解自己

378
00:20:13,910 --> 00:20:15,650
So,your Aunt Lily called Amanda.
所以Lily阿姨把Amanda叫回来

379
00:20:15,650 --> 00:20:19,110
All right,people,gather around. Let's make a memory.
好了 大家凑紧点 我们留个念

380
00:20:19,610 --> 00:20:21,970
Okay,Marshall - Marshall,try this.
Marshall Marshall 试试看这招

381
00:20:21,970 --> 00:20:23,970
Keep your eyes closed until the last second,
闭上眼睛 一直到最后一秒

382
00:20:23,970 --> 00:20:26,350
- and when I say so,open them. - Okay.
- 我说睁开 你再睁开 - 好

383
00:20:26,570 --> 00:20:28,100
Hey,Barney,is that a hole in your suit jacket?
Barney 你的外套上是不是有个洞?

384
00:20:28,100 --> 00:20:30,030
What? Where?
什么? 哪儿?

385
00:20:30,030 --> 00:20:32,040
Now,Marshall!
就现在 Marshall!

386
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:34,390
Damn it!
该死!

387
00:20:38,410 --> 00:20:40,740
Ted,name that bitch.
Ted 这婊子叫什么

388
00:20:41,240 --> 00:20:43,310
Birth... a? Bertha?
生...? Bertha?

389
00:20:43,310 --> 00:20:45,550
No,it was my birthday.
不对 你是想说生日

390
00:20:45,550 --> 00:20:48,680
Your brain makes associations in a very obvious way.
你脑子的联想模式太简单了

391
00:20:49,100 --> 00:20:52,410
All right,people. Gather around. Let's make a memory.
好了 大家凑一起 我们留个念

392
00:20:53,240 --> 00:20:57,090
Hey,Robin,what's in this dip you made? 'Cause it tastes like...
那个 Robin 你在蘸酱里放了什么? 我尝出... 

393
00:20:57,530 --> 00:20:58,710
cilantro.
芫荽叶的味道

394
00:20:58,710 --> 00:21:03,310
And you know that cilantro makes me...
你知道芫荽叶会让我...

395
00:21:03,690 --> 00:21:05,010
Yes!
太好了!

